title: You will always remember your First Ride Home – Britax B-Agile 3 & B-Safe 35 Travel System
description:
Designed for safety & contoured for baby to create the ultimate travel system.

The B-Safe 35 infant car seat & B-Agile 3 stroller combination delivers unmatched crash protection for your baby. The quick-fold B-Agile 3 stroller come fully loaded with our innovative CLICK & GO feature, a quick and secure connector allowing you easily move the B-Safe 35 from your car to your stroller.

Because... They were "Made for Each Other".

asset.author: Britax Child Safety, Inc
